r5547 | dschuff@google.com | Fri Jun 03 09:22:58 PDT 2011

Changed paths:
 M http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/chrome/trunk/src/native_client/tools/llvm/driver/pnacl-dis.py?r1=5547&amp;r2=5546&amp;pathrev=5547
 M http://src.chromium.org/viewvc/chrome/trunk/src/native_client/tools/llvm/driver/driver_tools.py?r1=5547&amp;r2=5546&amp;pathrev=5547

Use Semaphore instead of Event for synchronization of driver threads.
 (this allows the driver to block instead of spinning)
Allow RunWithLog args to override stderr logging
Don't process stdout/stderr redirect through python loop; instead dump directly out to the file object
Bypass line-by-line handling of stdout for pnacl-dis
 (this makes pnacl-dis fast enough that you don't want to gouge your eyes out)

